中睇下呼和浩特站既浮誇<br />\n對比起以前係勁咗好多<br />\n<br />\n利申: 個人意見 非專案人士<br />\nbtw已經好少聽新歌 歡迎補充"},{"pid":"73c93cfcdb53f5eb0c19131353da776c2948270d","tid":609293,"uid":167484,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T08:02:00.000Z","msg":"兩位都係好歌手<br />\n但個人較喜歡單春<br />\n佢是但唱一首已經好有感覺 唔使造作<br />\n反而覺得軒仔較著重技巧 唱唔出真誠<br />\n<br />\n非專業"},{"pid":"6448626ad74b8fb30f07cfe9b7f505d2560c30e2","tid":609293,"uid":9732,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T08:09:48.000Z","msg":"軒仔未可以去到e神好似傾計咁唱"},{"pid":"9092bcd5186b102a3946ec1f0e1551ae7e064072","tid":609293,"uid":23147,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T08:22:49.000Z","msg":"唔知正皮定負皮好 兩個我都好鐘意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"272ce0d2b47e8bf9a36420032c72e58ca50b06a1","tid":609293,"uid":162549,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T12:21:34.000Z","msg":"其實我唔信佢係gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd7ee1dd399e7a3668b3e0c2665ec3c4ccf071a9","tid":609293,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T12:24:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"84db40a210758bf9a75b517f215283717201dd97","tid":609293,"uid":36754,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T12:49:00.000Z","msg":"單春勝在太多神曲 人來人往,shall we talk, K歌之王,最佳損友呢堆 首首都唱入心底裏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a55dc5ad77ff288b69e2b5d230663ef907f94878","tid":609293,"uid":162549,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"84db40a210758bf9a75b517f215283717201dd97","tid":609293,"uid":36754,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T12:49:00.000Z","msg":"單春勝在太多