6:57.000Z","msg":"ching J 開韓紅?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T12:24:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T06:44:08.000Z","msg":"下 點會唱唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9e933a9f1ada7d04d90023a0b10397bd6d7151c","tid":609293,"uid":174882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c47b6066b37d5e9394dd517ae55ac8597fe7d95","tid":609293,"uid":162549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T02:13:02.000Z","msg":"把聲又溫柔 又靚仔 唱歌又好聽有感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唱live仲好聽過cd <br />\n雖然單春多k歌 但軒仔首首歌都好難唱<br />\nEason? 不了<br />\n張敬軒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n陳奕迅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/29/100349_b78adf9b18bdb04798b90ae5645891dc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F29%2F100349_b78adf9b18bdb04798b90ae5645891dc.png&h=7a403597&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/29/100351_951ff829149981e34016098cd6e55f07.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F29%2F100351_951ff829149981e34016098cd6e55f07.png&h=e76a41d2&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T06:45:29.000Z","msg":"軒仔多佢一粒蛋蛋  確實係好過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b17c0b6417b046c7fd2ecf97778ff842f424a29","tid":609293,"uid":124785,"like":4,"dislike":10,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T13:59:28.000Z","msg":"其實大家知唔知ＥＡＳＯＮ　係用講野把聲黎唱，　<br />\n<br />\n姐係唱歌同講野係同一把聲，　發音，腔調一樣 (唔知叫唔叫&quot;喉嚨聲&quot; )<br />\n<br />\n而軒仔係用其他身體部位黎扮聲　（我估佢係用後顎骨 同後鼻黎發)<br />\n<br />\n佢平時講野同唱歌係兩個發聲黎, <br />\n<br />\n因為EASON 天生把聲就咁唱都好聽, 加上佢係聲樂畢業, <br />\n<br />\n知道點樣運用佢本身把聲黎唱歌好聽<br />\n<br />\n軒仔話佢用本身把聲唱歌係唔會好聽, 唔係佢唔令聲 (佢天生都係令聲, 不過係女人聲,<br />\n<br />\n佢同ＥＡＳＯＮ　唱同一粒音，你會覺得軒仔好似高音Ｄ咁)<br />\n<br />\n同埋好多歌手都係扮聲出黎, 就算JOEY 都係扮,<br />\n<br />\n可以用講野聲唱歌GE 歌手唔多, e.g.張學友... 軒仔講過一兩個, 但我唔記得<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nＰ。Ｓ。　我個人就覺得軒仔正過ＥＡＳＯＮ　因為佢高音令Ｄ　同優雅Ｄ，仲有海豚音，<br />\n　　　　　　同埋佢識作歌作詞，個人又多情感，　同ＦＡＮＳ　又ＣＬＯＳＥ"}]}